 2 [0001] Op Expense / Liability — Charged to credit
 3 [0010] Non-Op Expense / Asset — Amortization, loss
 4 [0011] Non-Op Expense / Liability — Interest accrued
 5 [0100] Op Income / Asset — Got paid for work
 6 [0101] Op Income / Liability — Earned deferred revenue
 7 [0110] Non-Op Income / Asset — Interest, grant, gain
 8 [0111] Non-Op Income / Liability — Debt forgiven
 9 [1000] Asset / Liability — Borrowed, repaid
10 [1001] Asset / Equity — Owner invested/withdrew
11 [1010] Liability / Equity — Debt to equity
12 [1011] Asset / Asset — Internal transfer
13 [1100] Liability / Liability — Reclassify debt
14 [1101] Equity / Equity — Year-end close
Back
EOF
)

    local choice
